description:
The date & time that the [place](../place.json) or [subEvent](./subEvent.json) ends, as an ISO-8601 date. For example `2021-05-17T22:00:00+00:00`.

Required on places when using one of the following calendarTypes:

- `single`
- `multiple`
- `periodic`

Always required on subEvents.
title: place.endDate
